      "content": "yo, i'm working on a new horror anthology and i need some ideas for settings. i want to move away from the classic haunted mansions and stuff. can u help me brainstorm some 'urban legend' style settings that feel gritty and scary? like places in a city that people are actually afraid to walk through at night?",
