      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "1. Abandoned subway tunnels often rumored to be haunted, frequented by looters and unwelcome spirits.\n2. Crumbling warehouses in an industrial district, known to be the meeting places for shady night-time activities and supernatural occurrences.\n3. Dystopian streets with graffiti-covered buildings, said to hide hidden demons and dark rituals.\n4. Old, unlit cemeteries located in densely populated areas, going undisturbed by even the dead of night.",
